center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ngoi sao Messi kinh doanh mua khach san sang o Ibiza hinh anh\" title=\"Ng\u00f4i sao Messi kinh doanh mua kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n sang \u1edf Ibiza h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/Ngoi-sao-Messi-kinh-doanh-mua-khach-san-sang-o-Ibiza-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Theo The Sun, Messi kinh doanh mua Hotel Es Vive m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n sang tr\u1ecdng n\u1eb1m b\u00ean b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n c\u00f3 52 ph\u00f2ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 525 b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam. Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean MiM Ibiza Es Vive sau khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Barca mua l\u1ea1i, n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ngoai be boi ngoai troi, khach san cua Messi con co quay bar tren tang thuong.\" title=\"Ngo\u00e0i b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Messi c\u00f2n c\u00f3 qu\u1ea7y bar tr\u00ean t\u1ea7ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/messi2-7487-1522312898.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ngo\u00e0i b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Messi c\u00f2n c\u00f3 qu\u1ea7y bar tr\u00ean t\u1ea7ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"The Sun cho biet, Messi cung hoc tap doi thu C. Ronaldo kinh doanh khach san. Chan sut Real cung co hung thu mua bat dong san o hon dao nghi mat noi tieng Ibiza va lan nay M10 da nhanh chan dau tu truoc.\" title=\"The Sun cho bi\u1ebft, Messi c\u0169ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 C. Ronaldo kinh doanh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Real c\u0169ng c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa mua b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u1edf h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Ibiza v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y M10 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/messi3-1876-1522312898.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">The Sun cho bi\u1ebft, Messi c\u0169ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 C. Ronaldo kinh doanh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Real c\u0169ng c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa mua b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u1edf h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Ibiza v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y M10 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sieu sao Bo Dao Nha da khai truong hai khach san mang ten Pestana CR7 o que nha Funchal va Lisbon.\" title=\"Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng hai kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mang t\u00ean Pestana CR7 \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Funchal v\u00e0 Lisbon.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/messi4-9075-1522312898.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng hai kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mang t\u00ean Pestana CR7 \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Funchal v\u00e0 Lisbon.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C. Ronaldo co tham vong mo chuoi khach san tuong tu o Madrid, New York va  Marrakesh o Maroc.\" title=\"C. Ronaldo c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng m\u1edf chu\u1ed7i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf Madrid, New York v\u00e0  Marrakesh \u1edf Mar\u1ed1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/messi7-7998-1522312898.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C. Ronaldo c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng m\u1edf chu\u1ed7i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf Madrid, New York v\u00e0  Marrakesh \u1edf Mar\u1ed1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao 33 tuoi vua phan dau het minh tren san co, vua ban ron voi cong viec kinh doanh, quang cao hinh anh chuan bi cho cuoc song khi chia tay bong da.\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u1eeba b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng khi chia tay b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/messi5-7579-1522312898.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u1eeba b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng khi chia tay b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Voi viec mua khach san, Messi muon day manh thuong hieu MiM, chuan bi cong viec kinh doanh sau khi giai nghe.\" title=\"V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mua kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, Messi mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u MiM, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh sau khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/messi6-2677-1522312898.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mua kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, Messi mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u MiM, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh sau khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"639","checkdouble":"183147"},{"date":"15:23 30/03","title":"B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco b\u1ecb d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/ban-gai-tien-ve-isco-bi-doa-giet.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@fo