\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Kim Chi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t t\u1edd Naver Sport \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cDanh ti\u1ebfng s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 l\u00e0n kh\u00f3i thu\u1ed1c. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec\" - Naver Sport b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bao Han khen thay tro Park Hang Seo sau tran hoa Jordan hinh anh\" title=\"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n khen th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Bao-Han-khen-thay-tro-Park-Hang-Seo-sau-tran-hoa-Jordan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e1o H\u00e0n khen th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo d\u00f5i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u2018c\u1eeda tr\u00ean\u2019 Jordan, t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trang b\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c mi\u00eau t\u1ea3:\u00a0\u201cSau k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi gi\u00fap tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Asian Cup. Tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Naver Sport c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i K-League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Incheon v\u00e0 Gangwon. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0\u00a0l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh t\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-dt-viet-nam-can-cai-thien-nhung-gi-de-tien-xa-tai-vck-asian-cup-2019-168-183017.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/Bao-Han-khen-thay-tro-Park-Hang-Seo-sau-tran-hoa-Jordan-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-dt-viet-nam-can-cai-thien-nhung-gi-de-tien-xa-tai-vck-asian-cup-2019-168-183017.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019?</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan cho th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m trong 9 th\u00e1ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang UAE tham d\u1ef1 VCK...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"629","checkdouble":"183169"},{"date":"17:04 30/03","title":"Neymar b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3, k\u1ecbp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/26/neymar-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-than-ky-kip-tham-du-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0