0ea nh\u00e0 Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c sau ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 3. Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n ban \u0111\u1ea7u cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb UOL Esporte, Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho PSG ngay cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4 n\u00e0y. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Amiens, Rennes v\u00e0 Caen \u1edf Ligue 1. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Coupe de France.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Neymar, PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 4, 6 tu\u1ea7n sau ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec PSG m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Ligue 1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Neymar. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 mong mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay nh\u01b0ng PSG s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb trang UOL, Neymar mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh cho th\u1ea5y anh \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i si\u00eau \u00e2m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Neymar t\u1ea1i Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-bac-bo-ke-hoach-sa-thai-hlv-emery-197-183103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/28/psg-bac-bo-ke-hoach-sa-thai-hlv-emery.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-bac-bo-ke-hoach-sa-thai-hlv-emery-197-183103.html\">PSG b\u00e1c b\u1ecf k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch sa th\u1ea3i HLV Emery</span><br>\r\n<span>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Antero Henrique c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Unai Emery v\u1eabn l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 2, trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 c\u1ee7a PSG tr\u01b0\u1edbc Marseille t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 27 Ligue 1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil b\u1ecb \u0111au khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n 10 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft n\u1ee9t \u1edf x\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ed1 5 b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft n\u1ee9t l\u1edbn \u1edf x\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eefa b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n. Cu\u1ed9c ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn Neymar ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao Neymar s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"628","checkdouble":"183155"},{"date":"06:16 31/03","title":"HLV PSG mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1ec1 Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/21/hlv-psg-thong-bao-ngoi-sao-neymar-binh-phuc-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last