ck;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao Neymar s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 World Cup 2018, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/neymar-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-than-ky-kip-tham-du-world-cup-197-183155.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ng\u00f4i sao Neymar</strong></span> b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd t\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1i Paris Saint-Germain.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Neymar \u0111ang \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 \u0111i k\u00e8m r\u1ea1n x\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Marseille 3-0 c\u1ee7a PSG t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u201cng\u1ed3i ch\u01a1i x\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng li\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV PSG mang thong tin ngoi sao Neymar binh phuc chan thuong hinh anh\" title=\"HLV PSG mang th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00f4i sao Neymar b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/hlv-psg-thong-bao-ngoi-sao-neymar-binh-phuc-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ng\u00f4i sao Neymar b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Emery th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Neymar di\u1ec5n ra nhanh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 xa d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p (Coupe de la Ligue) v\u1edbi Monaco v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSG \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1eeb Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Neymar trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d, Emery th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cT\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t sinh g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft (vs Monaco). Neymar s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i n\u00f3 v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Paris trong v\u00f2ng 2 ho\u1eb7c 3 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/neymar-chan-thuong-dt-brazil-khong-con-la-chinh-minh-439-182842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/26/neymar-chan-thuong-dt-brazil-khong-con-la-chinh-minh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/neymar-chan-thuong-dt-brazil-khong-con-la-chinh-minh-439-182842.html\">Neymar ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110T Brazil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</span><br>\r\n<span>Leroy Sane cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Neymar ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia Ph\u00e1p (Coupe de France) v\u1edbi Caen v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 18 th\u00e1ng 4 t\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 PSG gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 8 th\u00e1ng 5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-tuc-world-cup/neymar-chan-thuong-dt-brazil-khong-con-la-chinh-minh-439-182842.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ng\u00f4i sao Neymar</strong></span> b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u1ede ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Nga, h\u1ecd n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng E v\u1edbi Costa Rica, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Serbia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/neymar-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-than-ky-kip-tham-du-world-cup-197-183155.html\">Neymar b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3, k\u1ecbp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-tite-brazil-dang-hoc-cach-song-khong-neymar-184-183022.html\">HLV Tite: Brazil \u0111ang h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/su-that-ve-viec-ngoi-sao-neymar-gay-chia-re-psg-197-182940.html\">S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Neymar g\u00e2y chia r\u1ebd t\u1ea1i PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/neymar-ra-dieu-kien-de-chiu-cho-chuyen-nhuong-real-mua-neymar-180-182921.html\">Neymar ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u201cd\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu\u201d cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/neymar-chan-thuong-dt-brazil-khong-con-la-chinh-minh-439-182842.html\">Neymar ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110T Brazil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/puyol-neymar-co-the-gia-nhap-real-madrid-184-182768.html\">Neymar r\u1eddi PSG ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"627","checkdouble":"183176"},{"date":"09:56 30/03","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, Buffon l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/truoc-dai-chien-buffon-len-tieng-khen-ngoi-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin: