{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League gi\u1eefa Juventus v\u00e0 Real, Gianluigi Buffon khen ng\u1ee3i Cristiano Ronaldo.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t anh ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 17 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real </strong></span>v\u00e0o Top 3 La Liga v\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truoc dai chien, Gianluigi Buffon khen ngoi Cristiano Ronaldo hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, Gianluigi Buffon khen ng\u1ee3i Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Truoc-dai-chien,-Gianluigi-Buffon-khen-ngoi-Cristiano-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng La Liga, Ronaldo \u0111ang t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 22 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Messi 2 b\u00e0n. \u1ede Champions League, CR7 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 8 tr\u1eadn, c\u1ef1u sao M.U v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Barca \u1edf La Liga, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf Champions League \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Gianluigi Buffon khen ng\u1ee3i Cristiano Ronaldo</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Real Madrid s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Juventus. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p nhau trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon phat bieu ve Ronaldo\" title=\"Buffon ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/truoc-dai-chien-buffon-len-tieng-khen-ngoi-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gianluigi Buffon ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League gi\u1eefa Juventus v\u00e0 Real, Gianluigi Buffon khen ng\u1ee3i Cristiano Ronaldo: \u201cTheo th\u1eddi gian, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y di chuy\u1ec3n \u00edt h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ronaldo</strong></span>, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Ronaldo lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\u201d, Gianluigi Buffon khen ng\u1ee3i Cristiano Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/juventus-42.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Juventus </strong></span>tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Champions League l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Real c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, Juventus ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d,</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/750-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"626","checkdouble":"183123"},{"date":"20:30 30/0