ign: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Las Palmas, HLV Zinedine Zidane ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 Isco s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin toi 303 Mourinho duoc hien ke Alexis Sanchez toa sang hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 303 Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf Alexis Sanchez t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/thuc-hu-chuyen-alexis-sanchez-bi-co-lap-o-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alexis Sanchez g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Man Utd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuan Sebastian Veron cho r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n Alexis Sanchez ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Man Utd, Jose Mourinho n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Football Espana, Atletico Madrid \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Paulo Dybala c\u1ee7a Juventus. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Griezmann ra \u0111i, Atletico s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi mua Dybala \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1c b\u1ecf th\u00f4ng tin Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n thu\u1ebf khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Paris Saint Germain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u loan tin Ph\u00e1p mi\u1ec5n thu\u1ebf cho Neymar nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y r\u1eddi Barcelona trong h\u00e8 2017.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng Barcelona chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Sevilla. &quot;Leo&quot; kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong hai giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f9ng \u0110T Argentina v\u00ec l\u00fd do s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Petr Cech ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Chelsea sang Arsenal b\u1edfi mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yannick Carrasco ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid t\u1edbi CLB Dalian Yifang (Trung Qu\u1ed1c) b\u1edfi mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, nh\u1eb1m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yannick Carrasco toi Trung Quoc de gianh suat du World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Yannick Carrasco t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/carrasco.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yannick Carrasco t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nQua vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 da m\u00e0u \u1edf \u0110T Ph\u00e1p b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Nga, Lilian Thuram cho r\u1eb1ng FIFA c\u1ea7n h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City, HLV Sam Allardyce cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Pep Guardiola \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng The Citizens.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League, Jesse Lingard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man Utd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i Premier League, thay v\u00ec mang t\u00e2m l\u00fd bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-hagl-43-u19-chonburi-u19-quoc-te-2018-325-183168.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/tong-hop-u19-hagl-43-u19-chonburi-u19-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-hagl-43-u19-chonburi-u19-quoc-te-2018-325-183168.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 HAGL 4-3 U19 Chonburi (U19 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nLi\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc (0-2 r\u1ed3i 1-3) song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 hay trong 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 b\u00e0n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (B\u00