dbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng u\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i tr\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5 v\u00e0 h\u00fat shisha.&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-nga-13-phap-giao-huu-quoc-te-329-182964.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">\u0110T Nga t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb &quot;soi&quot; r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Ngo\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, \u0110T Nga c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 doping khi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u00e2n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e2y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c th\u1ec3 thao Nga th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Nga tai World Cup 2018 cam cac cau thu uong tra khong qua kiem duyet va hut shisha.\" title=\"\u0110T Nga t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u1ea5m c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 u\u1ed1ng tr\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qua ki\u1ec3m duy\u1ec7t v\u00e0 h\u00fat shisha.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/dt-nga-tai-world-cup-2018-ra-thiet-quan-luat-cam-uong-tra-va-hut-shisha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Nga t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u1ea5m c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 u\u1ed1ng tr\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qua ki\u1ec3m duy\u1ec7t v\u00e0 h\u00fat shisha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, RFU v\u1eeba ra v\u0103n b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gi\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nga kh\u00f4ng u\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i tr\u00e0 ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5, h\u00fat shisha hay d\u00f9ng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 t\u1eeb Trung Qu\u1ed1c hay Nam M\u1ef9. Khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00ednh v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i n\u0103m 2015, Youcef Belaili - m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Algeria - \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec d\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00ednh trong cu\u1ed9c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/scandal-doping-nga-khong-anh-huong-den-world-cup-2018-421-174704.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m doping</span>. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 cho bi\u1ebft d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m khi c\u00f9ng h\u00fat shisha v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c, tr\u00e0 hay th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hay bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t World Cup 2018 minh b\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00f3a \u0111i nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u00e2n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e2y. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ngo\u1ea1i giao, \u0111e d\u1ecda kh\u1ee7ng b\u1ed1 hay n\u1ed7i lo v\u1ec1 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 Anh cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 n\u1ed9i c\u00e1c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, do li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn nghi \u00e1n c\u1ef1u \u0111i\u1ec7p vi\u00ean Sergei Skripal b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tien-thuong-world-cup-2018-cau-thu-duc-xach-dep-cho-tay-ban-nha-421-183101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/tien-thuong-world-cup-2018-cau-thu-duc-xach-dep-cho-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tien-thuong-world-cup-2018-cau-thu-duc-xach-dep-cho-tay-ban-nha-421-183101.html\">Ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng World Cup 2018: C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c x\u00e1ch d\u00e9p cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng World Cup 2018 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 800.000 euro n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"624","checkdouble":"183171"},{"date":"07:57 31/03","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 31/3: Coutinho su\u00fdt tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/12/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-313-coutinho-suyt-tro-tha