p \u0111\u1ed3ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i Gareth Bale. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng Coutinho t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 142 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bong da sang ngay 313 Coutinho suyt thanh nguoi Real hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 313 Coutinho su\u00fdt th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/goc-nhin-tu-khi-nao-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-coi-ti-hon-nhu-khong-lo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y Coutinho sang Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>West Ham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 sao M.U. </strong>West Ham \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Sam Johnstone l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Joe Hart v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Man United. Trong khi Hart v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Adrian ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9, Johnstone l\u1ea1i \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Aston Villa m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. West Ham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi s\u0103n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c. </strong>T\u1edd Kicker c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft ngo\u00e0i Arsenal, nh\u1eefng Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno. Arsenal xem c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Petr Cech v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec anh d\u00f9 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u00e1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Bernd Leno\" title=\"thu mon Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/real-mua-thu-mon-moi-thay-cho-de-gea-courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Atletico v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Leno</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>PSG t\u00ednh ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t v\u00ec Oblak. </strong>L\u00fd do Atletico ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua mua Leno nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 b\u1edfi m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain. \u0110\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jan Oblak t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Atletico. Ngo\u00e0i PSG, nh\u1eefng Chelsea v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng \"l\u0103m le\" c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng. </strong>Dean Henderson \u0111ang t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Manchester United v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u01a1i cho Shrewsbury Town t\u1ea1i League One m\u00f9a n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Dean Henderson\" title=\"thu mon Dean Henderson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/thu-mon-dean-henderson-roi-mu-trong-mua-he-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Henderson t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>V\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn M.U v\u00e0 Barca.</strong> Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Man United v\u00e0 Barcelona trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham. Trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Mauricio Pochettino g\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t anh ch\u01a1i cho Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18/2 trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 v\u1edbi Rochdale t\u1ea1i FA Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV PSG mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1ec1 Neymar.</strong> HLV Unai Emery c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao Neymar s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 World Cup 2018, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ng\u00f4i sao Neymar b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd t\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1i Paris Saint-Germain.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"623","checkdouble":"183184"},{"date":"11:43 30/03","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110i\u1ec1u Barca c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/goc-nhin-dieu-barca-can-la-ket-qua-khong-phai-da-dep.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position