12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Valverde kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady?</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Valverde l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ernesto Valverde t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Olympiacos t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009, \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0&hellip; \u0111\u1ec3 thua. G\u1ea7n ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m sau, \u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi &ndash; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Barcelona-37.html\">Barcelona</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu l\u00e0 th\u1eadt, b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i c\u00e3i, nh\u01b0ng HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, HLV n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng b\u1ecb c\u00e1c cules nghi ng\u1edd \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. CLB m\u00e0 Valverde d\u1eabn d\u1eaft l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Athletic Bilbao, v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB trung b\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng &ldquo;y\u1ebfu \u1edbt&rdquo; v\u1ec1 Valverde, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi\u1ebfn cho BL\u0110 Barca c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng d\u00e1m hy v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loi choi Barca - Valverde Khi ket qua quan trong hon phong cach hinh anh\" title=\"L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca - Valverde Khi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n phong c\u00e1ch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/valverava.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Valverde b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V nh\u00e0 nghi ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia mong \u0111\u1ee3i khi m\u1eddi v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Bilbao gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, cho d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea1i gia, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Basque v\u1eabn n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e1u l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t, l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Valverde. L\u00e0 4-3-3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 \u1edf Camp Nou, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 HLV n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. H\u00e3y nh\u00ecn xem khi \u0111\u00f3 Barca l\u00e0 ai? M\u1ed9t CLB \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga v\u00e0o tay <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Real-Madrid-29.html\">Real Madrid</span>, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juve \u1edf Champions League, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Cup Nh\u00e0 vua \u0111\u1ec3 an \u1ee7i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Luis Enrique ra \u0111i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t si\u00eau sao Neymar r\u1eddi b\u1ecf. Barca nh\u01b0 r\u1eafn m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u00f3i m\u1ea5t nanh v\u00e0 loay hoay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n nh\u1edb, phong tr\u00e0o \u0111\u00f2i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bartomeu t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c c\u00f2n l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u00e0o&hellip; &ldquo;Wenger Out&rdquo; l\u00fac n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00f3i kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eb9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, Ernesto Valverde \u0111em v\u1ec1&hellip; Paulinho, m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i&hellip; Trung Qu\u1ed1c, b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u1ecfi Tottenham v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t, phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Xavi. C\u00e1c C\u0110V Barca th\u00ec v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, \u0111\u00f2i mang Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f2i Coutinho c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn. Ch\u1eb3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, g\u00e3 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111em v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e1&hellip; g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i (150 tri\u1ec7u euro bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed). Qua v\u00e0i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, Dembele&hellip; l\u0103n ra ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 Barca tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 &ldquo;c\u00e1i m\u00e1ng l\u1ee3n&rdquo; gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng&hellip;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loi choi Barca duoi thoi Valverde da thay doi khi ho mat Neymar\" title=\"L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Valverde \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/valveneymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Valverde \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Real Madrid \u0111\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ed5, nh\u01b0ng Valve-lona \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t Neymar, ch\u1eb3ng sao, khi Valverde v\u1eabn \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebf - <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/lionel-messi-44368.html\">Lionel Messi</span>. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Barca c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1eed khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u0169i \u0111inh ba \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. M\u1ea5t Neymar, h\u1ecd gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. 4-3-3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o d\u0129 v\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng Valverde \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t 4-4-2 c\u00f2n hay h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paulinho b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t, ch\u1eb3ng sao. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Trung Qu\u1ed1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eb1ng Xavi. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, anh gi\u00fap c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Barca thay \u0111\u1ed5i. D\u1eb9p b\u1ecf l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tiki-taka t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Pep, Enrique v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ngang s\u00e2n, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Paulinho.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Real-Madrid-29.html\">Real Madrid</span> s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u00fang. H\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ch\u1eb3ng sai. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. M\u1ed9t Real-\u0111\u1eb9p-m\u1eaft \u0111ang k\u00e9m Barca-th\u1ef1c-d\u1ee5ng 1 b\u00e0n \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tay-ban-nha-c180-p1.html\">La Liga</span> (73 so v\u1edbi 74), c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh (th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi g\u1ea5p 3 l\u1ea7n Barca). C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san b\u1eb1ng tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid 0-3 Barca\" title=\"Real Madrid 0-3 Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/valvereal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f3 ai c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ch\u01b0a ch\u1ecbu b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi l\u00e1 th\u0103m may m\u1eafn Roma, Barca \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0103n 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid, Man City hay Bayern Munich c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0o nho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng ai trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng Valve-lona v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, ch\u00ednh K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u0169ng chu\u1ed1c nh\u1ee5c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu 0-3 \u0111\u1ea5y th\u00f4i, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Zidane \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1eaft c\u1eed Kovacic theo k\u00e8m Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 mong t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Barcelona-37.html\">Barcelona</span> th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng hy v\u1ecdng Ernesto Valverde t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd, ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd ch\u1ee9 ch\u1eb3ng ai kh\u00e1c, \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\">Champions League</span>, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch Cup Nh\u00e0 vua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfm ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em La Liga v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia. H\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn Liverpool b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Coutinho v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng, Barca c\u00f2n \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng ai nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Chi ti\u00eau qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0? Ch\u1eb3ng sao, v\u00ec th\u1eddi gian s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00e1c cules c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 Arsenal, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u00f2n c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ea?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barca-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-suc-khoe-cua-messi-180-183114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/hlv-barca-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-suc-khoe-cua-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barca-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-suc-khoe-cua-messi-180-183114.html\">HLV Barca c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Messi</span><br>\r\nMessi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Sevilla v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"622","checkdouble":"183137"},{"date":"16:43 30/03","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 30/03","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-3003.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opac