ay:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 30/03.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Barca hot nhat ngay 3003 hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3003 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-hot-nhat-ngay-3003-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Diario Gol, n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi PSG \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid thay v\u00ec tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ee5 Griezmann</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</strong></span> Barca 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. M.U v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca lo l\u1eafng khi MU \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Umtiti</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti\" title=\"Umtiti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/14/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-273-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca so s\u1ee3 Umtiti s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thei Sport, BL\u0110 Barca \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo l\u1eafng khi MU \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 54 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Barca v\u1ee5 Griezmann</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Atletico Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca</strong></span>, n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n anh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Umtiti v\u00e0 Luke Shaw</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1edbi Old Trafford n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luke Shaw theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"621","checkdouble":"183158"},{"date":"21:35 30/03","title":"Isco r\u1eddi Real Madrid, Zidane c\u00f3 ph\u1ea