5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zinedine Zidane tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed theo Diario Gol \u0111\u01b0a tin, 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/5-cau-thu-real-muon-day-isco-ra-di-180-180497.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Isco r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span></span> g\u1ed3m Cristiano Ronaldo, Gareth Bale, Karim Benzema, Luca Modric v\u00e0 Casemiro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco cua Real\" title=\"Isco cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/isco-roi-real-madrid-zidane-co-phai-la-thu-pham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Isco r\u1eddi Real Madrid b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a HLV Zidane.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c Isco r\u1eddi Real Madrid l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. L\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng T\u00e2y Ban Nha 6-1 Argentina, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/toa-sang-o-doi-tuyen-isco-len-tieng-chi-trich-real-madrid-421-182985.html\" target=\"_blank\">Isco tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c HLV Zidane</span> kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u00ecnh \u1edf Real Madrid, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui t\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n TBN.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean, HLV Zidane l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh: &quot;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a Isco kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i phi\u1ec1n l\u00f2ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u1eadu c\u1ea5y hi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zizou kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t trong m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, HLV Zidane c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Isco c\u00f9ng Sergio Ramos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Las Palmas v\u00ec th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Las Palmas s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 23h30 (31/3) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-tbn-hy-vong-isco-se-bung-no-trong-mau-ao-real-madrid-180-183000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/hlv-tbn-hy-vong-isco-se-bung-no-trong-mau-ao-real-madrid.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-tbn-hy-vong-isco-se-bung-no-trong-mau-ao-real-madrid-180-183000.html\">HLV TBN: Hy v\u1ecdng Isco s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Isco l\u1eadp hat-trick, \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"620","checkdouble":"183173"}]}